  "title": "Insurance Broker",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Delivering excellent client experience throughout the advisory journey</li><li>Understanding and assessing clients’ need for protection</li><li>Developing and implementing insurance solutions for clients</li><li>Developing long-term client engagement</li><li>Assisting in claims and policy servicing</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>To be successful in this position, you will be someone who:</p><ul><li>Enjoys financial planning work as well as interactions with clients</li><li>Possess good understanding of insurance products and services</li><li>Is driven, tenacious and possess a strong sense of work ethics</li><li>Is a licensed financial adviser or on track to getting one</li><li>Has good interpersonal & communication skills</li><li>Has a diploma or bachelor degree in any discipline</li><li>Has prior working experience in a similar role could be an advantage</li></ul>",
